SELECT count(*) FROM [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[horizon_nsip_relevant_representation] where contactId in 
(select representedId from [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[sb_nsip_representation])



Select representationId, count(*)
from odw_harmonised_db.dbo.sb_nsip_representation
where isactive='Y'
group by representationId
having count(*) > 1



Select contactid, caseuniqueid, count(*)
from odw_standardised_db.dbo.horizon_nsip_relevant_representation
where ingested_datetime = (select max(ingested_datetime) from [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[horizon_nsip_relevant_representation])
group by contactid, caseuniqueid
having count(*) > 1

select distinct representationId from odw_harmonised_db.dbo.sb_nsip_representation
where isactive='Y'
